module.exports = subtract

/**
 * Subtracts vector b from vector a
 *
 * @param {vec2} out the receiving vector
 * @param {vec2} a the first operand
 * @param {vec2} b the second operand
 * @returns {vec2} out
 */
function subtract(out, a, b) {
    out[0] = a[0] - b[0]
    out[1] = a[1] - b[1]
    return out
}
